pageContext.claim: “I think they're talking about Feinstein. Can you believe that? Now, was that the worst body language, honestly? In other words, did she leak it? A hundred percent. No, no, I don't want to get sued. Ninety-nine percent.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence that Sen. Dianne Feinstein leaked the letter accusing Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh of sexual misconduct. Feinstein emphatically denied she had leaked.
